description:
We’ve been talking about “I Will GO” for months, but what is it really and how will the Church do the research to see if it’s been successful? How do the KPI’s, or Key Performance Indicators, fit in? What will it say about who we are as a Church and what’s next? Find out in this new episode of ANN In-Depth. 

You can learn more about the church's strategic plan and KPI's at iwillgo2020.org. 

For this week's episode, we are joined by David Trim and Jeff Scoggins. David Trim is the Director of Archives, Statistics, and Research for the General Conference of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. Jeff Scoggins is the Planning Director for Adventist Mission.
